  "texts": [
    "However, CoT is susceptible to the Clever Hans effect, where the LMM generates wireless policies, and the human in the loop, aware of right vs. wrong solutions, inadvertently guides the LMM.",
    "The responsibility for accuracy, if achieved, lies with the human in the loop.",
    "This framework raises concerns when the human cannot verify the answer to the planning problem themselves.",
    "However, in a wireless network, to ensure automated network operation, we cannot afford to rely on human intervention.",
    "Therefore, a promising approach entails the LMM critiquing its predictions through self-reflection capability and iteratively self-improving."
  ],
